. New competitive game modes - V.I.P, Capture the flag, Hostage rescue, Thief escape, Capture mission and more! New fun game modes - Zombie escape, Jailbreak, Murder and more! (check the complete list in our Wiki page http://ogat.gamepedia.com/GameModeHUGE GAMEMODE EXPANSION!Prepare to join a new series of huge game modes like "Thief Town", "Zombie Apocalypse", "Life", "Hunger Games" and more! These game modes include a lot of new features like: Dynamic daylight based on realistic night and day cycle. Dynamic Weather system. Survival Features - Sickness, hunger, thirst and fatigue. MMO features - Inventory, crafting, farming, harvesting, hunting, fishing and more. Bigger games with persistent world. Vehicles. Buildable environment - House, base, traps, farming and crafting structures and more. Living world - Animals, creatures and NPC characters.						
